<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Transaction Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #2196F3;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .transaction-details {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196F3;
        }
        .contact-info {
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .final-amount {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #2196F3;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>ðŸ“‹ Transaction Confirmation</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{buyerName}},</h2>
        
        <p>This email confirms the successful completion of your auction transaction. All details are listed below for your records.</p>
        
        <div class="transaction-details">
            <h3>Transaction Summary:</h3>
            <p><strong>Item:</strong> {{auctionTitle}}</p>
            <p><strong>Auction ID:</strong> #{{auctionId}}</p>
            <p><strong>Transaction Date:</strong> {{transactionDate}}</p>
            <p><strong>Seller:</strong> {{sellerName}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="final-amount">
            Final Purchase Amount: ${{finalAmount}}
        </div>
        
        <div class="contact-info">
            <h3>Seller Contact Information:</h3>
            <p><strong>Name:</strong> {{sellerName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{sellerEmail}}</p>
            <p><em>Please coordinate delivery and payment arrangements directly with the seller.</em></p>
        </div>
        
        <div style="background-color: #e8f5e8; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h3>Important Reminders:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>An invoice has been sent to both parties via email</li>
                <li>Please save this email as proof of purchase</li>
                <li>Coordinate payment and delivery details with the seller</li>
                <li>Contact our support team if you encounter any issues</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <p>Thank you for using AuctionBid! We hope you enjoy your purchase and look forward to seeing you in future auctions.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The AuctionBid Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an official transaction confirmation from AuctionBid Platform</p>
        <p>Keep this email for your records</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
